        Siuniaev
        - Gambler Cat

        Instant Zoomies - Horror Starter Pack Free

        Synty
        - Ancient Empire



        2D

        Vector Dividers Collection

        upklyak
        (freepik) - Ground cracks on land isolated



        VFX

        Unity
        Technologies - Particle Pack



        <b>Audio

        </b>

        Freesound
        - Various Sounds

        Pixabay - Various Sounds

        Uppbeat - Music



        <b>Music

        </b>

        Brock
        Hewitt - In The Silence

        Monument Music - Love Story



        <b>Fonts

