        Craiyon
        - 2D art

        Piclumen - 2D art

        Suno - Music



        <b>Other
        Tools Used

        </b>

        Audacity

        Gimp

        Blender

        Unity



        <b>Game
        Jam

        </b>

        This game was created for the

        Dungeon
        Crawler Game Jam 2025





'
